	(882,149,'team_headline_1','THE COMPANY'),
	(883,149,'_team_headline_1','field_5525c4eba151b'),
	(884,149,'team_description','Circuit Media LLC creates, publishes and disseminates advertising, news and information through print and online media. Our clients are business, legal and governmental entities as well as their respective clients.\r\n\r\nFounded in 2002 by Colorado attorney Rebecca Askew, Circuit Media publishes newspapers, reports, guides, and lists focusing on the legal and governmental industries. Our products and services enable our clients to tastefully and effectively communicate and compete in a rapidly changing environment.\r\n\r\nCircuit Media has been certified as an 8(a), WOSB, and EDWOSB entity by the Small Business Administration; an approved contractor with the Government Printing Office; a DBE and ACDBE business with the City and County of Denver; and SBE with the Regional Transportation District. It was also chosen by the SBA as an Emerging 200 business for 2011. This designation is only given to 200 companies nationwide that show a high potential for growth and sustainability.\r\n\r\nWe are located near Broadway and I-25  in downtown Denver. Our employees are versed in both PC and Mac environments, and our designers specialize in the Adobe Creative Suite. Our employees are college graduates with specialized degrees in photography, journalism, creative writing, marketing, advertising, graphic design, and law.'),
