	(98,1,'2015-04-07 01:55:11','2015-04-07 01:55:11','Mobile CRS 2014 provides easy and affordable access on your mobile device and tablet to all titles, articles, and sections of the Colorado Revised Statutes, as amended.\n\nThe current version reflects the official version of the statutes for 2014 with changes passed at the Second Regular Session of the 69th General Assembly. Mobile CRS 2014 supplements all 44 of your physical volumes of the statutes and is a perfect companion for your “on-the-go” reference needs.\n\nTop features of the app include:\n\n• The ability to reach all 30,000+ sections of the Colorado Revised Statutes with no Internet connection required;\n• Full keyword search of the text;\n• Ability to add notes and bookmarks to sections as well as to email sections and notes;\n• Quickly delete all bookmarked sections;\n• View all notes at once, and send email backups of all notes at once.\n\nIf you enjoy using Mobile CRS 2014, please consider leaving positive feedback in the app store. If you have difficulties using the application, please let us know at support@comlabmobile.com.\n\nThis product is produced in partnership with <a href=\"http://mobilecrs.wordpress.com/\">COM-LABS</a>.','Digital CRS','','inherit','open','open','','77-autosave-v1','','','2015-04-07 01:55:11','2015-04-07 01:55:11','',77,'http://localhost:8888/Jhorton_CircuitMedia/77-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
